   "source": [
    "# Sampling with replacement\n",
    "\n",
    "Consider $n$ objects and making $k$ choices from them, one at a time with replacement (i.e., choosing a certain object does not preclude it from being chosen again). Then there are $n^k$ possible outcomes (based on [multiplication rule](multiplication-rule.ipynb))."
   ]
  }
